oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Swimming pool, Dunbar Cave, Idaho Springs, Clarksville, Tenn.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color tinted and enhanced photograph of a large public swimming pool located near Dunbar Cave State Park. There are numerous people swimming and others watch from benches along the perimeter. A building and lake are visible in the distance. Features a divided back and narrative on reverse. There is a (partially obscured) logo for E.C. Kropp Co. around the stamp box in the upper right corner. Postcard printed on linen. Note: there is surface damage on the back side of this postcard. [No. 29339N]
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Swimming pools; People; Fences; Trees
